pageContext.claim: “By the end of the year, it'll be mostly finished. We may add another 50 miles that was unplanned for in certain areas that are little bit tough. So, we will make that determination. But the wall is built.”
pageContext.analysis: It's not clear what Trump is talking about. No plans for an additional 50 miles of barriers have been announced, though construction crews are racing to finish the barrier ahead of the election.
